caption: I love this place. I have been coming here over 10 years. You choose 4 different things and they put them on your plate which comes with rice and soup. They do not speak very good English, so it takes a lot of finger pointing, but that's also fun. And it's cheap, the whole thing costs $5.50 now. It used to be $3 back in the day. I normally get pork belly, kombu kelp, daikon radish and clams. They are excellent!
